Columns.Name: DunsNumber
Columns.Description: Dun & Bradstreet (D&B) provides a D-U-N-S Number, a unique nine digit identification number, for each physical location of your business.

Columns.Name: ReportPurchaseDate
Columns.Description: The purchase date of the report.

Columns.Name: BranchAndDivisionIndicator
Columns.Description:
Indicates that the business is a branch or division of a parent company,

Ex:
- Yes

Columns.Name: NaicsCode
Columns.Description:
The business NAICS code.

Ex:
- 323110
Commercial Lithographic Printing

Columns.Name: FinancialStrengthScore
Columns.Description:
The Financial Strength Indicator is calculated using either the Net Worth or Issued Capital of the Subject Company. 

Ex:
- 3A

Columns.Name: CompositeCreditAppraisalScore
Columns.Description:
The composite credit appraisal of the business.

Ex:
- 4

Columns.Name: PriorDbRatingScore
Columns.Description:
The prior DB score of the business.

Ex:
- 3A4

Columns.Name: PaymentActivityCurrencyName
Columns.Description:
The reference currency of payment activities.

Ex:
- USD

Columns.Name: AverageHighCreditAmount
Columns.Description: The average high credit amount extended to the business.

Columns.Name: HighestCreditAmount
Columns.Description: The highest credit amount extended to the business.

Columns.Name: TotalHighestCreditAmount
Columns.Description: The total highest credit amount extended to the business.

Columns.Name: DunBradstreetFinancialConditionTypeId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of a Dun Bradstreet Financial Condition Type.

Columns.Name: DunBradstreetHistoryStatusTypeId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of a Dun Bradstreet History Status Type.
